{
  "id": "adv_event_2304_01_05",
  "title": "ずっと\nライバル",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "ただいま……って、みんなどうしたの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm back… Hey‚ what's going on with everyone?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 5.1333333332999995,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-living-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 266.66666669999995
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ski001.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃんから話は聞きました\nもう……大丈夫なんですよね？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We heard from Sakura-chan what happened.\nAre you feeling better now?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 5.3597963651,
      "endTime": 11.266666666699999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "うん、さっき{user}さんにも\n話してきた。……心配掛けて、ごめん",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ I just talked to {user} earlier.\n…Sorry for worrying you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.4970301628,
      "endTime": 18.1472570418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "元気になったみたいで良かったわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Seems like you're feeling better.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.3605904896,
      "endTime": 20.8732889492,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "まったく、これで一安心ですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ we can breathe a sigh of relief.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 21.0732890446,
      "endTime": 24.5356473286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-szk001.m4a",
      "text": "アンチの言葉を気にしないのは、難しい。けど……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ignoring the words of the haters is difficult. But…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.7423139572,
      "endTime": 30.2050804138,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_04-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "私達がいるから……一緒に頑張ろう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're here for you… Let's do our best together‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 30.4184137185,
      "endTime": 34.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "みんな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 34.645396185,
      "endTime": 35.9411547781,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "とてつもないクオリティのステージを見せて、理不尽な\n批判なんて吹き飛ばしてみせればいいんですのよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Show them an incredible stage‚\nblow away the unfair criticism!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.14115479,
      "endTime": 44.0333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-szk002.m4a",
      "text": "すずちゃんが燃えてる……メラメラ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-chan is fired up… Burning!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.2828734001,
      "endTime": 47.6466148456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ありがとう\nでも……すずの言う通りね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ thank you.\nBut… Suzu is right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.8399481695,
      "endTime": 54.4793360632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "私達十人で……最高のステージにしよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's make the best stage… with all ten of us.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.686002644,
      "endTime": 58.572714766,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "そういえば、「月ストとサニピで競い合おう」って話を\nさくらとしたんだって？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Speaking of which‚ Sakura said something about\n\"Moon Tempest and Sunny Peace competing‚\" right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.7860481185,
      "endTime": 64.9872727316,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ktn006.m4a",
      "text": "仲良くやるのも大事だけど、競い合う意識を持てば\nきっと私達はもっと成長出来ると思うから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's important to get along‚ but I think we can grow more from\nhaving a competitive mindset.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.1806061031,
      "endTime": 72.0393591168,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ski",
      "speakerName": "白石沙季",
      "speakerNameEn": "Saki",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-saki.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-ski002.m4a",
      "text": "仲良くしつつも競い合う……なんだか燃えますね\n負けないからね、千紗",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Getting along while competing… That's inspiring.\nWe won't lose‚ Chisa.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 72.226025669,
      "endTime": 78.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
      "speakerNameEn": "Chisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-chisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-chs001.m4a",
      "text": "お姉ちゃん……私だって、負けないから！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Big sis… I won't lose either!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.872742947,
      "endTime": 83.46666666670001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "szk",
      "speakerName": "兵藤雫",
      "speakerNameEn": "Shizuku",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-shizuku.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-szk003.m4a",
      "text": "白石SISTERSのバチバチ、ふたたび……！\nたぎる……！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The Shiraishi Sisters rivalry‚ once again…!\nExciting…!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.8174326183,
      "endTime": 88.6666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "よーし、今日の夕ご飯の出来上がり！\nみんな……あ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Alright‚ dinner's ready tonight!\nEveryone… Oh.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.0270420632,
      "endTime": 97.693708857,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "琴乃ちゃん、すっかり元気になったみたいね\n……良かった",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Kotono-chan‚ you seem completely better now.\n…I'm glad.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.0070406359,
      "endTime": 103.4784011286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "うん……遙子ちゃんのおかげだよ、ありがとう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah… Thanks to you‚ Haruka-chan. Thank you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.7384000064,
      "endTime": 108.0074980975,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "怜。ここの振り付け、もう少しダイナミックにしても\nいいのではなくて？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Rei‚ wouldn't it be better to make the choreography here\na little more dynamic?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.1341504654,
      "endTime": 115.5666585286,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "みんなの体力や柔軟性を考えると\n動きの幅はこれくらいにした方がいいんじゃない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Considering everyone's stamina and flexibility‚\nwouldn't it be better to keep the range of movement about this much?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 115.709261028,
      "endTime": 123.0465854566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "舐めないでくださいまし！　月ストは日々成長し続けて\nいるんですのよ。サニピだってそうでしょう？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't underestimate us! Moon Tempest continues to\ngrow every day. Sunny Peace does too‚ right?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.2599186182,
      "endTime": 130.8666605632,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "これくらいの動きでくじけるほど\nやわに出来てはいませんわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We're not so fragile that we'd collapse\nfrom movements like these!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1648119528,
      "endTime": 135.4007958411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "分かった。一応……柔軟性はすずに合わせてたんだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Understood. I was trying to accommodate your flexibility to Suzu‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 135.6930830876,
      "endTime": 143.1416769902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "え",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 143.3416769902,
      "endTime": 144.2007958411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "でも、すずがそう言うなら応えない訳にいかないわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But if you say so‚ Suzu‚ I can't just ignore it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5730212063,
      "endTime": 149.13412917440002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "あ、えっと、その、怜……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Uh‚ um‚ Rei…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 149.4488045227,
      "endTime": 153.36746250779998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "極端な無理はさせられないから\n可動域のぎりぎりを攻める感じで……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because I can't force extreme strain‚\nwe'll push the limits of the range of motion…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.6827221961,
      "endTime": 159.8007958411,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05/sud_vo_adv_event_2304_01_05-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほどほどにしてくださいましね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "P-Please it's enough…!",
